Package: eurobarometer
Type: Package
Title: Eurobarometer Survey Harmonization
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Daniel Antal
Maintainer: Daniel Antal <daniel.antal@ceemid.eu>
Description: The package import and converts GESIS Eurobarometer SPSS files 
    and converts them to programatically friendly data files. The
    variable names, quesitons and questionnaire items are harmonized
    with comprehensive numerical, factor and character representation.
    This helps the creation of integrated data files from different
    surveys.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
